      <!-- Purpose -->
      <div class="border-b border-sna-gray-line pb-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3 text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Purpose</h2>
        <p>SNA Acoustic Consultancy, through its branch SNA Acoustic Consultancy, responsible for this website, makes this document available to users in order to comply with the obligations set forth in Law 34/2002 on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE), and to inform all website users of the conditions of use. Any person accessing this website assumes the role of user, committing to the strict observance and compliance of the provisions included herein, as well as any other applicable legal provision. SNA Acoustic Consultancy reserves the right to modify any information that may appear on the website, without any obligation to give prior notice to users, it being understood that publication on the website is sufficient.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Liability -->
      <div class="border-b border-sna-gray-line pb-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3 text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">SNA Acoustic Consultancy disclaims any liability arising from information published on its website, provided that such information has been manipulated or introduced by a third party.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">SNA Acoustic Consultancy is not responsible for the information and content stored, including but not limited to, forums, chats, blog generators, comments, social networks, or any other medium that allows third parties to publish content independently on the SNA Acoustic Consultancy website.</p>
        <p>This website has been reviewed and tested to function correctly. In principle, correct operation can be guaranteed 365 days a year, 24 hours a day. However, SNA Acoustic Consultancy does not rule out the possibility of certain programming errors, or force majeure events, natural disasters, strikes, or similar circumstances that make access to the website impossible.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Intellectual property -->
      <div class="border-b border-sna-gray-line pb-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="border-l-2 border-primary pl-3 text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Intellectual and industrial property</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">The website, including but not limited to its programming, editing, compilation, and other elements necessary for its operation, designs, logos, text and/or graphics, are the property of SNA Acoustic Consultancy or it holds an express licence or authorisation from the authors.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Regardless of the purpose for which they are intended, total or partial reproduction, use, exploitation, distribution, and commercialisation requires in all cases prior written authorisation from SNA Acoustic Consultancy.</p>
        <p>SNA Acoustic Consultancy recognises the corresponding intellectual and industrial property rights in favour of their holders, and their mere mention or appearance on the website does not imply the existence of any rights or liability on the part of SNA Acoustic Consultancy.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Applicable law -->
