        <p class="mb-4">For the resolution of all disputes or questions related to this website or activities carried out on it, Spanish legislation shall apply, to which the parties expressly submit, with the corresponding courts according to the user's domicile being competent for the resolution of all disputes derived from or related to its use.</p>
        <p>Likewise, SNA Acoustic Consultancy and the user may submit their disputes to the arbitration provided for in arbitration and consumer protection legislation, and to extrajudicial dispute resolution procedures established through codes of conduct or other self-regulation instruments.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer info -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-sna-gray-line text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        <p>SNA Consultoría Acústica</p>
        <p>Torre Europa, Paseo de la Castellana, 95, planta 29, 28046 Madrid</p>
        <p>Phone: 91 838 78 66</p>
        <p>Email: info@snaconsultoriaacustica.com</p>
